Description: Cylinder seal of black steatite: perforated through the centre and broken off at one end. The seal is inscribed. Good condition.
Curator's comments: Bibliography: P. Kaplony, 'Die Inschriften der Ägyptischen Frühzeit III (Wiesbaden, 1964), pl. 112, abb. 618; P. Kaplony, 'Die Inschriften der Ägyptischen Frühzeit II (Wiesbaden, 1964), 1171.
Previous owner: Previous owner/ex-collection: Rev George Denis Nash
